OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has urged Labour MPs
OL,8,Fto reject a bid for a parliamentary
OL,9,Fsleaze inquiry into the Lord Mandelson
OL,10,Fvetting row as he faces another moment
OL,11,Fof peril for the future of his
OL,12,Fpremiership.
OL,14,FThe Commons will vote on Tuesday on
OL,15,Fwhether the Privileges Committee
OL,16,Fshould consider if the Prime Minister
OL,17,Fmisled the House over the way the
OL,18,Fformer Labour grandee's appointment as
OL,19,FUS ambassador was handled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FA large-scale effort appeared under
OL,8,Fway by Monday evening to rally support
OL,9,Ffrom the back benches, with former
OL,10,FLabour prime minister Gordon Brown
OL,11,Falso urging the party to back Sir Keir.
OL,13,FIt is understood Labour MPs are being
OL,14,Fwhipped to reject the motion to refer
OL,15,FSir Keir to the committee after
OL,16,FCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,17,Fallowed a vote on the issue following
OL,18,Frequests from Tory leader Kemi
OL,19,FBadenoch and other senior MPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FAt a packed meeting of the
OL,8,FParliamentary Labour Party on Monday
OL,9,Fevening, the Prime Minister sought to
OL,10,Fdismiss the attempt to launch an
OL,11,Finquiry as a "stunt" by political
OL,12,Fopponents trying to inflict damage
OL,13,Fbefore the May elections.
OL,15,F"I have responsibility for being
OL,16,Ftotally transparent with you, with
OL,17,FParliament and the British public," he
OL,18,Ftold Labour parliamentarians.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@TO]wD@AOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,F"I take that very seriously as well.
OL,8,FBut this is not about a lack of
OL,9,Ftransparency.
OL,11,F"This is a political stunt by our
OL,12,Fopponents who want to bring us down,
OL,13,Fobscure our message, stop us getting
OL,14,Fon with our work.
OL,16,F"And the timing tells you everything
OL,17,Fnine days before local elections."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FHe claimed the Conservatives had put
OL,8,Fforward "totally baseless" and
OL,9,F"absolutely ridiculous" accusations
OL,10,Fagainst him and insisted the motion on
OL,11,FTuesday was "pure politics", adding:
OL,12,F"We need to stand together against it."
OL,14,FSir Keir added: "When we stick
OL,15,Ftogether and fight together we are so
OL,16,Fmuch stronger."
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@ZO]qD@AOUqD@WO]sD@MOUsD@[O]tD@
OL,26,AAOUtD@gO]vD@QOUxD@OO]
