CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FThe Government also took the unusual
OL,8,Fstep on Monday of publishing a letter
OL,9,Ffrom former cabinet secretary Sir
OL,10,FChris Wormald to the Prime Minister,
OL,11,Fin which he said he had concluded the
OL,12,F"appropriate processes were followed"
OL,13,Fin both the appointment and sacking of
OL,14,Fthe peer.
OL,16,FIn the message dated September 16, Sir
OL,17,FChris, who conducted a review into
OL,18,FLord Mandelson's appointment, said he
OL,19,Fwould "keep this under review if any
OL,20,Ffurther evidence emerges".
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@eO]{D@GOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FBut Sir Keir's insistence that "no
OL,8,Fpressure existed whatsoever in
OL,9,Frelation to this case" appeared to be
OL,10,Fcontradicted by a key figure in the
OL,11,Fvetting process for the ambassadorship
OL,12,Fto the Foreign Affairs Select
OL,13,FCommittee on Monday evening.
OL,15,FAccording to a letter from the Foreign
OL,16,FOffice drafted in consultation with
OL,17,FIan Collard, the official said he
OL,18,F"felt pressure to deliver a rapid
OL,19,Foutcome" to the clearance procedure.
OL,26,@oD@`OUqD@VO]zD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FThis was in light of "regular contact
OL,8,Ffrom No 10 to the FCDO (permanent
OL,9,Funder-secretary's) office," the letter
OL,10,Fsaid, though Mr Collard did not
OL,11,Fpersonally speak to Downing Street
OL,12,Fcolleagues and "does not assess that
OL,13,Fthis pressure influenced professional
OL,14,Fjudgment that was reached by himself
OL,15,For his team".
OL,26,@oD@VOUqD@[O]tD@POUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
