OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has been accused of
OL,8,Fmisleading MPs by saying that "full
OL,9,Fdue process" was followed in
OL,10,Fappointing Lord Mandelson, who was
OL,11,Fgiven developed vetting status despite
OL,12,Ffailing security checks.
OL,14,FThe Foreign Office, under then top
OL,15,Fcivil servant Sir Olly Robbins cleared
OL,16,Fhim despite red flags raised by
OL,17,Fexperts at the UK Security Vetting
OL,18,Fagency responsible for the checks.
OL,26,@pD@_OUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FMr Collard, who briefed Sir Olly on
OL,8,Fthe vetting findings, also did not see
OL,9,Fthe UKSV file recommending clearance
OL,10,Fbe denied, according to the letter
OL,11,Fpublished on Monday.
OL,13,FInstead, he received an oral briefing
OL,14,Ffrom officials which led him to
OL,15,Fbelieve Lord Mandelson's case was
OL,16,F"borderline" and that "the risks could
OL,17,Fbe mitigated," the evidence said.
OL,19,FTory leader Mrs Badenoch called for
OL,20,FLabour MPs to back the referral to the
OL,21,FPrivileges Committee.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@LO]xD@WOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FShe said: "The Prime Minister misled
OL,8,Fthe House of Commons repeatedly. He
OL,9,Fappointed a national security risk and
OL,10,Ffriend of a convicted paedophile to be
OL,11,Four ambassador in Washington, our most
OL,12,Fsensitive diplomatic post.
OL,14,F"He pretended that full due process
OL,15,Fwas followed for this appointment. It
OL,16,Fwas not.
OL,18,F"He has blamed the appointment on
OL,19,Fofficials when the blame can only be
OL,20,Fplaced at his own door."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@AOUzD@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FMr Brown urged Labour to unite in
OL,8,Ffocusing on putting "the needs of the
OL,9,Fcountry first" in a statement on
OL,10,FMonday evening.
OL,12,F"Whatever the parliamentary games at
OL,13,FWestminster, what the country expects
OL,14,Fof everyone in Labour is to focus on
OL,15,Fthe priorities of the British people,
OL,16,Fwhich is what Keir Starmer is doing
OL,17,Fand for which he deserves all our
OL,18,Fsupport," he said.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@NO]tD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,8,Fsaid Labour MPs must be given a free
OL,9,Fvote on Tuesday.
OL,11,F"Even Boris Johnson didn't block his
OL,12,FMPs voting for scrutiny," he said.
OL,14,F"If Keir Starmer has misled the House
OL,15,Fand the public, he must be held to the
OL,16,Fsame standard that we should expect of
OL,17,Fany prime minister."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@YO]vD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage told the
OL,8,FPress Association: "There's no doubt
OL,9,Fhe's misled Parliament more than once
OL,10,Fand not just on this issue, on others
OL,11,Fas well."
OL,13,FHe added: "Starmer's future will be
OL,14,Fdecided by the elections on May 7 and
OL,15,Fif Reform do as well as I think we can
OL,16,Fin the old Labour areas, that will be
OL,17,Fthe end of him."
OL,26,@pD@TOUsD@IO]uD@KOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FDowning Street has said the Government
OL,8,Fis already committing to two
OL,9,Fparliamentary processes ` questioning
OL,10,Ffrom the Foreign Affairs Committee
OL,11,Fabout Lord Mandelson's vetting and a
OL,12,FCommons motion forcing the publication
OL,13,Fof documents relating to his
OL,14,Fappointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FChief Secretary to the Prime Minister
OL,8,FDarren Jones said that more than 300
OL,9,Ffiles would have been passed by the
OL,10,FCabinet Office to Parliament's
OL,11,FIntelligence and Security Committee by
OL,12,Fthe end of Monday as part of the
OL,13,Fsecond process.
OL,15,FThese have been judged to be
OL,16,Fprejudicial to "national security or
OL,17,Finternational relations," he told MPs
OL,18,Fon Monday, and include "a number that
OL,19,Fare relevant" to the peer's vetting
OL,20,Ffor the prestigious Washington posting.
OL,26,@xD@POUyD@YO]zD@XOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FThe ambassadorship ended after nine
OL,8,Fmonths last September when Lord
OL,9,FMandelson was sacked over the extent
OL,10,Fof his links to paedophile financier
OL,11,FJeffrey Epstein.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, the Foreign Affairs
OL,14,FCommittee is also due to hear from Sir
OL,15,FKeir's former chief of staff, Morgan
OL,16,FMcSweeney, widely regarded as a
OL,17,Fprotege of Lord Mandelson, who
OL,18,Fresigned in February.
OL,20,FThe committee will also hear from Sir
OL,21,FOlly's predecessor, Sir Philip Barton.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FSir Olly, who was sacked by Sir Keir
OL,8,Ffor not disclosing the security
OL,9,Fconcerns to ministers, gave evidence
OL,10,Fto the cross-party group of MPs last
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FSir Olly said he was told the security
OL,14,Fexperts who carried out the vetting
OL,15,Fdeemed Lord Mandelson a "borderline"
OL,16,Fcase and leaned towards recommending
OL,17,Fthat clearance be denied, but the
OL,18,Fofficial approved his developed
OL,19,Fvetting status with mitigations put in
OL,20,Fplace.
OL,26,@wD@YOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777334614
OL,3,CStarmer urges Labour MPs to vote
OL,4,Cagainst parliamentary probe into
OL,5,CMandelson row
OL,7,FDowning Street has said the findings
OL,8,Ffrom UK Security Vetting, the agency
OL,9,Fwhich carried out the checks, were
OL,10,Fmore clear-cut, describing Lord
OL,11,FMandelson as of "high concern" and
